window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An alien race decides humanity’s fate: Eradication. They didn’t count on someone rising to challenge their decree. </p> <p>Constantine had forsaken his family name and birthright. At 28-years old, he’d escaped Earth to help terraform Mars. </p> <p>An empire’s heir went missing just as the universe’s greatest threat announces itself. </p> <p>War Games will decide who represents humanity in this extinction level struggle. Constantine is summoned. </p> <p>With little training but abundant talent, can Constantine win these games? If he does, will he be a force in the coming war? Or is it already too late for humanity? </p> <p>Let the games begin. </p> <p>You’ll love this epic space military saga, because the struggle is just beginning and the battles coming down the road are like nothing you’ve seen before. Get it now.</p>"; 
